    "id": 8404771209532,
    "title": "SeaKing Bait Board SK-E09 - Black (820mm x 460mm)",
    "body_html": "<p><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><meta charset=\"utf-8\">SeaKing SK-E09 (BLK)</p>\n<div data-mce-fragment=\"1\" data-content-field=\"excerpt\" class=\"ProductItem-details-excerpt\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Introducing the SeaKing SK-E09, a standout in the SeaKing Range now available in a sleek black gel </span><span>coat, a distinctive feature unique to bait boards. Crafted with an emphasis on ergonomic design, this </span><span>premium model boasts a spacious knife tray conveniently located at the front for quick access. </span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>It also </span><span>features a deep storage sink complete with a drain, ensuring practicality during fishing sessions. What <meta charset=\"utf-8\">sets the SK-E09 apart is its raised lip surrounding the sides and back, designed to securely hold items <meta charset=\"utf-8\">even in turbulent waters. Constructed from high-quality composite materials and outfitted with a UV </span><span>resistant PE plastic cutting board, this board is built for durability and longevity</span></p>\n<span></span><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-f00d8e6b-7fff-3500-c50d-7229ab8e3eda\"></b>\n</div>",
